    "It is clear that ca is a functor.",
    "Structure relations between bpol • [I, ⋅] and P 2 ⊂ (I), a sketchWe search for an \"isomorphism\" between bpol • [I, ⋅] and P 2 ⊂ (I) via an \"isomorphism\" between the functor ca ○ κ ∶ bpol • [I, ⋅] → bpol • [I, ⋅] and the functor identity1 bpol • [I,⋅].",
